				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2006/11/30/tfttf164-an-amazing-journey/" title="4:31 am" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2006-11-30T04:31:36+00:00">November 30, 2006</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/author/chris/" title="View all posts by Chris Marquardt" rel="author">Chris Marquardt</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
