<p><!--adsense-->Today Jon Miller talks about the film he made about a Mt. Everest expedition and that he has now turned into <a target="_blank" href="http://www.therestofeverest.com/">an amazing video podcast</a>, and we learn from Kavey about how to organize a listener get-together!<br />
